title: Asian Kung-Fu Generation - The Recording
description:
Got this off of youtube before it was taken down, I don't see it available anywhere else so I bestow upon you this gift. 

THE RECORDING AT NHK CR-509 STUDIO - LIMITED EDITION

Tracks	13
Length	01:06:11


Though it is considered as the band's first studio live album, "The Recording at NHK CR-509 Studio" is actually the band playing for a private program reserved for the suscribers at the NHK. The band has nothing to do with this album, it was fully made by "NHK" who are responsible for the most ugly booklet/design ever made, as well as the content chosen (15 % of the video recording were put on a DVD). The sales were a complete failure. Musically speaking, it's perfect as usual
